drive: invite: Usage: _build/macosx64/bin/infinit-drive --invite --name DRIVE --user USER [OPTIONS...]

Invite a user to join the drive:

Invite options:
  -n [ --name ] arg      Drive to invite the user to
  -u [ --user ] arg      Existing users to invite to the drive via user name
  -e [ --email ] arg     New users to invite to the drive via email
  --fetch-drive          Update local drive descriptor
  -f [ --fetch ]         Alias for --fetch-drive
  --push-invitations     Update remote drive descriptor and send invitations
  -p [ --push ]          Alias for --push-invitations
  --passport             Create passports for each invitee

Hidden options:
  --permissions arg      Set default user permissions to XXX
  -h [ --home ]          Creates a home directory for the invited user


